{"tid":1020094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"狠心父母虐4幼童「關狗籠＋淋屎尿」！冰箱上鎖不給飯吃","createTime":"2019-02-13T11:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T11:39:10.000Z","uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9d4fd630f8cb6d51a09018580e3258dc70ae421b","tid":1020094,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T11:30:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DzOTT_fX4AEjWVf?format=jpg&amp;name=900x900\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDzOTT_fX4AEjWVf%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D900x900&h=6cf8b6a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n美國德州12日爆發一起嚴重虐童案！有一對年僅24歲的年輕夫妻，竟然把4名5歲以下的兒女關在穀倉當中，其中把最年長的2名幼童關在狗籠裡，另外2名小孩則全身淋滿屎尿，誇張行徑讓當地警長相當痛心。幸運的是，4名幼童在接受醫院治療後已無大礙。<br />\n<a href=\"http://根據WPTV.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%A0%B9%E6%93%9AWPTV.com&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyEV3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=2ccefea5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">根據WPTV.com</a>報導，當地警方於12日當天接獲鄰居通報，隔壁穀倉傳來兒童以及一對男女的爭吵聲後，於上午7時20分，在穀倉內分別發現4名衣服破舊的幼童，其中最年長的5歲男童與4歲女童，一起被關在長寬高各90公分狗籠裡，另外3歲和1歲的男童則被淋滿糞便和尿液。<br />\n更可惡的是，雖然穀倉內藏有豐富的食物，但這對夫妻竟然把冰箱和櫥櫃上鎖，導致幼童們無法取得食物養分，只能默默待在穀倉內挨餓口渴。警長阿金（Lane Akin）難過地表示，這是他44年的職涯中見過最嚴重的虐童案，他從未遇過兒童被關在如狗籠一般的噁心環境中。<br />\n案件曝光後，4名幼童已經被帶到沃斯堡（Fort Worth）當地的兒童醫療中心治療。至於24歲女子和同居男友則遭到警方逮捕，並被指控4項危害孩童罪。據了解，女子是4名幼童的生母，其中一名幼童則是2人的親生骨肉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DzPZxpaV4AAgbrM?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDzPZxpaV4AAgbrM%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dsmall&h=1628fe1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DzPZxpaUwAAGrDu?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDzPZxpaUwAAGrDu%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dsmall&h=129057c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在得知此事後，許多網友憤怒之餘大罵2人，「試試看把他們關進狗籠裡一個月，不提供食物和水，看他們怎麼辦」、「如此殘忍的行為證實他們不配活在地球上」、「把小孩交給我吧，讓我來照顧」、「真是太邪惡了」、「為甚麼有人可以做出這麼殘忍的事」、「下地獄吧」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190213/1377212.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190213%2F1377212.htm&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyEV3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=09d9c43b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190213/1377212.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c47cba5568e5b69c2082fd24527d238fb8043a2f","tid":1020094,"uid":157197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T11:32:16.000Z","msg":"條友劈完友嚟？"},{"pid":"696cbab10c0c8e2fef480f3bf6fa137a68c6f7dd","tid":1020094,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T11:33:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"295da6c79fd58e9494e77d6e351ed1e7741c71b6","tid":1020094,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T11:35:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78199c9cdf335633690d07370a3c2460f1e56e78","tid":1020094,"uid":229789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T11:37:06.000Z","msg":"估錯國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b6c2f98f181ca20745899cc24a8e216052a9ce","tid":1020094,"uid":36134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T11:39:10.000Z","msg":"條仔好似有d亞裔血統<br />\n咁撚柒既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}